<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shinchan - Homepage</title>
</head>
<body>

    <header align="center">
        <img src="assets/shin-chan-banner.jpg" alt="Crayon Shinchan Banner" width="100%">
        <nav>
            <a href="#game">Shinchan: Shiro and the Coal Town Game</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            <a href="#characters">Characters</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            <a href="#favorite">Who's your favorite?</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <hr>

    <main>
        <section id="game" align="center">
            <h2>Shinchan: Shiro and the Coal Town</h2>
            <p><strong>(Available on: Nintendo Switch and Windows PC)</strong></p>
            <video src="assets/shinchan-and-the-coal-town.mp4" controls width="800"></video>
        </section>

        <br><br>

        <section id="characters" align="center">
            <h2>The Characters</h2>
            <table align="center" width="80%" cellpadding="10" style="text-align: center;">
                <tr>
                    <th width="33%"><h3>Shinnosuke Nohara (Shinchan)</h3></th>
                    <th width="33%"><h3>Misae Nohara (Mom)</h3></th>
                    <th width="33%"><h3>Hiroshi Nohara (Dad)</h3></th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-shinchan.png" alt="Shinchan" height="150"></td>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-misae.webp" alt="Mom" height="150"></td>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-hiroshi.webp" alt="Dad" height="150"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr valign="top">
                    <td>The mischievous 5-year-old protagonist known for his hilarious antics and love of choco chips.</td>
                    <td>Shinchan's short-tempered but loving mother, always trying to keep him in line.</td>
                    <td>The laid-back father who works at a company and enjoys his evening beer.</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <th><h3>Himawari (Sister)</h3></th>
                    <th><h3>Yukino Nohara (Shiro)</h3></th>
                    <th><h3>Toru Kazama</h3></th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-himawari.png" alt="Himawari" height="150"></td>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-shiro.png" alt="Shiro" height="150"></td>
                    <td><img src="assets/character-toru-kazama.webp" alt="Kazama" height="150"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr valign="top">
                    <td>The youngest of the Noharas. Loves shiny objects and brand-name goods. Smiles sideways, like Shinchan</td>
                    <td>The family dog — small, fluffy, and sometimes the most sensible member of the household.</td>
                    <td>The smart and responsible friend of Shinchan, often the voice of reason in the group.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </section>

        <br><br>

        <section id="favorite">
            <h2>Who's your favorite?</h2>
            
            <form action="#" method="POST">
                <label for="fav-char">Who's your favorite character?</label>
                <select id="fav-char" name="fav-character">
                    <option value="shinchan">Shinchan</option>
                    <option value="misae">Misae</option>
                    <option value="hiroshi">Hiroshi</option>
                    <option value="himawari">Himawari</option>
                    <option value="shiro">Shiro</option>
                    <option value="kazama">Kazama</option>
                </select>
                <br><br>

                <p><strong>Character not in the list? Write their name below:</strong></p>
                <label for="other-char">Your other favourite character:</label>
                <input type="text" id="other-char" name="other-character" placeholder="Enter character name">
                <br><br>

                <label for="reason">Why do you like this character?</label><br>
                <textarea id="reason" name="reason" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="State your reasons in a couple of lines..."></textarea>
                <br><br>

                <h3>Tell us a bit more about yourself</h3>
                
                <label for="username">Your Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="Enter your name">
                <br><br>

                <label>Your Gender:</label>
                <input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="male">
                <label for="male">Male</label> &nbsp;
                <input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="female">
                <label for="female">Female</label>
                <br><br>

                <label for="dob">Your Date of Birth:</label>
                <input type="date" id="dob" name="dob">
                <br><br>

                <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email">
                <br><br>

                <input type="submit" value="Submit">
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <br><br>
    <hr>

